Package requests

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CommandRequest
    this class is for defining a command line/lines request which can be identified by RequestsFactory and it can be annotated by Line.
    E2EValidationRequest
    this class is for defining E2E validation request which can be identified by RequestsFactory and it can be annotated by Items.
    EmailRequest
    this class is for defining a email/emails quest which can be identified by RequestsFactory and it can be annotated by Message.
    RestfRequest
    this class is for defining a restful webservice request which can be identified by RequestsFactory and it can be annotated by Auth Body Cookie Header Method URL UseSSL
    ScenarioRequest
    this class is for defining a scenario which can be identified by RequestsFactory and it can be annotated by Properties.
